---
title: Pork & Fennel Fettuccine with Garlic-Parsley Pangrattato
description: Salt and pepper, meat pie and sauce, pavlova and cream – some things just belong together! Now it’s time to add pork and fennel to that list, just taste the way the fragrant spice adds depth and flavour to tender pork mince in this pasta sauce. Top the whole thing off with a crisp pangrattato and Parmesan and that’s what we call a perfect match!
